      "amount": "3 tablespoons"
    },
    {
      "name": "All-Purpose Flour",
      "amount": "2 tablespoons"
    },
    {
      "name": "Vegetable Shortening",
      "amount": "8 tablespoons"
    },
    {
      "name": "Phyllo Dough Sheets",
      "amount": "18 sheets"
    },
    {
      "name": "Coconut Cream Pie Filling (Optional)",
      "amount": "1 cup"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 350°F (175°C).",
    "Combine cream cheese, tofu, coconut milk, vanilla extract, salt, and cinnamon in a mixing bowl. Mix well until smooth.",
    "In another bowl, mix coconut oil with flour and shortening until crumbly.",
    "Roll out phyllo sheets, layering them lightly coated with flour to prevent sticking.",
    "Place a heaped spoonful of the cream cheese mixture into each phyllo cup, followed by a scoop of coconut cream filling if using.",
    "Fold up the edges and seal tightly. Repeat until all dough cups are filled.",
    "Pre-bake for 10 minutes at 350°F (175°C).",
    "Brush with melted coconut oil or vegan butter. Bake an additional 20-25 minutes, or until golden brown.",
    "Serve warm and enjoy the comforting velvety texture of this delightful dessert."
  ],
